  body

    div(class='main-ct')
      div(class='frame')
        div(class='display')
          div(class='matrix-ct container')
            -for(var row=0; row<8; ++row)
              div(class='matrix-row')
                -for(var col=0; col<8; ++col)
                  div(class='matrix-cell')
          div(class='colorpicker-ct container')
            div(class='colorpicker')
          div(class='info-ct container')
            div(class='info')
              | <h1>pix.pub</h1>
              | <p>Whatever you draw here will instantly appear in a picture frame that is currently exhibited in a bar somewhere.</p>
              | <p>Made in <a href="http://www.fablabbudapest.com/" target="_blank">FabLab&nbsp;Budapest</a> by <a href="http://kunakos.ro/" target="_blank">Kún&nbsp;Ákos</a> and <a href="http://demetamas.com/" target="_blank">Deme&nbsp;Tamás</a>.</p>
              | <p><strong>Beta, man. Sooo very beta.</strong></p>
      div(class='buttons')
        div(class='button mirroring-toggle')
        div(class='button colorpicker-toggle')
        div(class='button info-toggle')

    script(src='https://cdn.firebase.com/js/client/2.2.1/firebase.js')
    script(src='https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.2.0/jquery.min.js')
